to stay away from her husband?

19
00:04:05,947 --> 00:04:08,415
I'm gonna plug up the hole
in that wall...

20
00:04:08,587 --> 00:04:12,216
and if I ever catch you again
peeking at me in my sleep...

21
00:04:12,387 --> 00:04:14,503
I'm moving into the
