23
00:04:20,027 --> 00:04:23,258
Let me talk with you.
I want to talk with you.

24
00:04:23,427 --> 00:04:27,545
Save your breath to drum up business
for your cotton gin...

25
00:04:28,227 --> 00:04:30,104
Close that door
so I can get dressed.

26
00:04:30,267 --> 00:04:31,416
Go on, get dressed.

27
00:04:31,587 --> 00:04:34,704
Not until you get on the other
side of that door and close it.

28
00:04:34,867 --> 00:04:37,984
