20th birthday.

32
00:04:46,587 --> 00:04:50,500
Sweet of you to remember.
Where's my birthday present?

33
00:04:51,027 --> 00:04:53,666
You'll get your birthday present...

34
00:04:53,907 --> 00:04:56,182
providing you haven't forgotten
the agreement between us...

35
00:04:57,067 --> 00:04:59,342
which comes due on that day.

36
00:05:01,347 --> 00:05:02,666
The agreement?

37
00:05:02,947 --> 00:05:04,539
Yes, the agreement.

38
00:05:04,707 --> 00:05:06,982
You swore on the Bible
to keep your side.

39
00:05:07,147 --> 00:05:08,466
If you kept yours.

40
00:05:08,627 --> 00:05:09,946
Have I laid a hand on you?

41
00:05:10,107 --> 00:05:12,416
Yes, as often as possible...

42
00:05:12,587 --> 00:05:16,785
Have I? Have I ever once
forced myself on you?

43
00:05:16,947 --> 00:05:21,259
As your husband, by law.
Or don't the law mean nothing to you?

44
00:05:21,427 --> 00:05:23,577
How about your side
of the agreement?

45
00:05:23,747 --> 00:05:27,456
You talked mighty big
when you were courting me...

46
00:05:27,627 --> 00:05:31,415
